     <body>
           <div type="panelGrp" xml:id="eg_0001">
              <cbml:panel n="1" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">
                 <cbml:caption>                    
                    <title rendition="#b #red #large #vertical">COPETIN  
                    </title>
                    <fw type="sig" place="lower-left">
                       POR  <lb/>
                       ERNESTO  <lb/>
                       FRANCO
                    </fw>
                 </cbml:caption>
                 <sound> rendition="#b #large" GGRRRRRRRR </sound>
                 <sound> @#*%#@ </sound>
                 <note type="panelDesc"> Copetin and Boy are sleeping on the street, covered
                    by newspapers. Boy snores loudly. Copetin has symbols of grumpiness over
                    his head.               
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="2" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">
                 <sound> rendition="#b #large" GRRRRR </sound>
                 <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#copetin"> 
                    ¡HUY  <lb/>
                    QUE DES-  <lb/>
                    GRACIA <lb/>
                    TAN TE- <lb/>
                    RRIBLE!                    
                 </cbml:balloon>
                 <note type="panelDesc"> Copetin is awake, clearly disturbed by
                    the boy's snoring. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="3" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">
                 <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#copetin">   
                    ¡ESTE CHINO DES- <lb/>
                    GRACIAO NO ME HA <lb/>
                    “DEJAO” DORMIR NI <lb/>
                    UN SEGUNDO CON <lb/>
                    SUS MALDITOS RON- <lb/>
                    QUIDOS!                    
                 </cbml:balloon>      
                 <note type="panelDesc"> Copetin is sitting up, clearly very disturbed by
                    the boy's snoring. 
                 </note> 
              </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="4" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">              
              <cbml:balloon rendition="#jaggies" type="speech" who="#copetin">
                 ¡DESPERTATE SO  <lb/>
                 ‘DESGRACIAO’ QU’ES-  <lb/>
                 TAS RONCANDO CO-  <lb/>
                 MUN CONGRESIS-  <lb/>
                 TA!                 
              </cbml:balloon>              
              <note type="panelDesc"> MCU of Copetin's head as he pokes the boy and yells
                 at him to wake up. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
              <cbml:panel n="5" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#anon_boy"> 
                 QU’QUE QUIE-  <lb/>
                 RES COPE?
              </cbml:balloon>
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#copetin">
                 !QU’ESTAS RON-  <lb/>
                 CANDO MUCHO  <lb/>
                 Y COMO NO TE CALLES TE VOY   <lb/>
                 A RAJAR LA ‘MULA’ OYES?      
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> Lateral MCU of boy's head and Copetin speaking. 
              </note>           
           </cbml:panel>       
              <cbml:panel n="6" characters="#anon_boy">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#anon_boy"> 
                 ¡PPERO COPE,  <lb/>
                 SI YO NO HE  <lb/>
                 ‘PEGAO’ LOS OJOS EN ‘TUA’  <lb/>
                 LA #@# NOCHE!                 
              </cbml:balloon>                    
              <note type="panelDesc"> Lateral MCU of boy's head as he speaks to Copetin.  and books.
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="7" characters="#copetin">
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" rendition="#jaggies" who="#copetin"> 
                 ¡LO QUE “NUÁS” “PE-  <lb/>
                 GAO” ES ESA COCHI-  <lb/>
                 NA JETA! AHORA  <lb/>
                 DUERMETE “CALLAO”!               
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> Lateral CU of Copetin as he speaks loudly.
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="8" characters="#anon_boy #copetin">
              <cbml:caption who="#narrator"> 
                 Y AL MOMENTICO…
              </cbml:caption>
              <sound> rendition="#b #large" GRRRRRRRRRR </sound>
              <sound> *#@#   <lb/>
                     #@#           
              </sound>   
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS of the two boys sleeping on the street. Boy is
                 snoring, and Copetin is grumbling about it.
              </note>                           
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="9" characters="#copetin">
              <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#copetin"> 
                 ¡CARAY, SE  <lb/>
                 M’ESTÁ OCU-  <lb/>
                 RRIENDO U-  <lb/>
                 NA IDEOTA  <lb/>
                 Y LA “MA-  <lb/>
                 CHA”!                 
              </cbml:balloon>                         
              <note type="panelDesc"> MCU of Copetin sitting up and scratching the back of his head
                 with his right hand.                  
              </note>              
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="10" characters="#copetin">
              <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#copetin"> 
                 ¡LE VOY A ME-
                 TER ESTA SIRE-  <lb/>
                 NA QUE ME RO-  <lb/>
                 BE’N EL LEY  <lb/>
                 EN LA JETA  <lb/>
                 Y… JA JA JE  <lb/>
                 JE E E E…!                   
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> Lateral MCU of Copetin sitting up and holding
                 a siren in his right hand as he grins in delight. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="11" characters="#sleepers #anon_woman">              
              <cbml:balloon rendition="#jaggies" type="speech" who="#sleepers">
                 HUY
           </cbml:balloon>  
              <sound rendition="#b #large"> 
                 AAAAEEEEIIIOO
              </sound>   
              <note type="panelDesc"> EWS shows loud siren noise coming from the background
                 into the night and startling sleepers in buildings, anonymous woman on the street, and
                 passengers inside a car.   
              </note>            
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="12" characters="#anon_boy">
              <sound rendition="#large"> 
                 EEEEIIIIIIIIOOOOUUUUU
              </sound>
              <cbml:balloon rendition="#b #large #center #red" type="feeling" who="#anon_boy">  
                  ?
              </cbml:balloon>              
              <note type="panelDesc"> MCU of anonymous boy sitting up to find himself with
                 a loud noise-making siren between his lips. He looks puzzled. 
              </note>
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="13" characters="#policeman #anon_boy">
              <cbml:balloon rendition="jaggies" type="speech" who="#policeman">  
                 ¡CON QUE TU ERES  <lb/>
                 EL GRACIOSO! VAMOS AL PERMANENTE POR  <lb/>
                 PERTURBAR LA PAZ  <lb/>
                 DEL BARRIO!
              </cbml:balloon>
              <cbml:balloon type="speech" who="#anon_boy">
                 P.PERO  <lb/>
                 Y.YO …NO  <lb/>
                 XX                
              </cbml:balloon>
              <note type="panelDesc"> Lateral WS shows silhouette of Policeman as he lifts
                 boy up in the air on the right of the frame. Boy looks very small and 
                 frightened. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel>
           <cbml:panel n="14" characters="#copetin">
              <cbml:balloon type="thought" who="#copetin"> 
                 ¡AHORA LES V’A  <lb/>
                 TOCAR EL TUR-  <lb/>
                 NO A LOS PO-  <lb/>
                 BRES DETENI-  <lb/>
                 DOS DEL PERMA-  <lb/>
                 NENTE!
              </cbml:balloon>
           <fw type="sig" place="lower-right">
              FRANCO
           </fw>
              <note type="panelDesc"> WS shows Copetin calmly lying on his back on the ground,
                 by himself, under sheets of newspaper. 
              </note> 
           </cbml:panel> 
        </div>
        <pb/>    
      </body>
